I am a-mazed! I affect You so much!
You thought of me from eter-nity past.
For me, You had sent Your beloved Son from heav’n,
And He gave Him- self for me on the cross;

Father, Your beau-ti-ful heart
Was pierced through with arrows!
O’ glorious! The Lord cried out ‘It is finished!’

The veil was rent; You dashed to me;
Em - braced me to Your heart;
Kissed me with kiss - es;
Rested on my neck You 're overjoy
You pre-pared a rich feast; You sang and danced;
Shouted for joy o-ver me, Your heart — was filled,
Embrac-ing me, ravished in love!
I am amazed! Infin - ite You are;
Out of love, You need me most
Yearning for me to be close to You
For- e’er hand in hand, live in love!

18-01-2004 awoke in sleep
UBC Palace Vancouver

For the great sal-vation, You gave Your all;
And for comforting man, humble You were.
For preaching the good news, on earth You trod;
It’s You who have loved me, my Lord!

